					<font size="12"/>
				</textElement>
				<text><![CDATA[Larger specimens may need to be bisected and appropriate portions selected to ensure adequate fixative penetration. In this case, the standard buffered formalin solution was changed periodically <br /><br /> <font color="orange"><b>'shall'</b></font>]]></text>
