				</textElement>
				<text><![CDATA[para1) The storage duration and temperature, typically in ambient temperature in routine archives, influence the DNA stability in FFPE tissue samples]]></text>
			</staticText>
		</band>
		<band height="68" splitType="Prevent">
			<staticText>
