		<band height="94">
			<staticText>
				<reportElement positionType="Float" x="25" y="0" width="545" height="94" uuid="5410593e-e736-4b65-853a-66e3e0ef37f2"/>
				<textElement textAlignment="Justified" verticalAlignment="Middle" markup="html">
					<font size="12" pdfFontName="net/sf/jasperreports/fonts/dejavu/DejaVuSerif-Italic.ttf" isPdfEmbedded="true"/>
				</textElement>
				<text><![CDATA[Lower storage temp. (2-8Â°C, -20Â°C) slow down the DNA degeneration process. If FFPE tissue is not stored dry, the DNA degradation can increase, and fungal and bacterial growth can be stimulated. There is evidence that the FFPE blocks can be analysed after 5 years or longer, if they are processed and stored appropriately.]]></text>
			</staticText>
		</band>
